txt.en: Ganglemód, ousted from her den by the Dheghûn, scuttles through the Drúadan forest in a blinding bitterness.
You have slain Ganglemód and vanquished a threat to the safety of all that dwell within Far Anórien.
Ganglemód can be found wandering the Drúadan Forest in Taur Drúadan.\n\nYou have encountered Ganglemód and should defeat the beast for the good of the people in Far Anórien.
